{
    "speakers": {
        "npc": {
            "name": "Bill",
            "face": {
                "type": "artificial",
                "modelType": "npc",
                "identifier": "cobblemon:supernerd",
                "isLeftSide": true
            }
        }
    },
    "pages": [
        {
            "id": "greeting",
            "speaker": "npc",
            "lines": [
                "Hola, soy Bill. ¿Y tú quién eres?"
            ],
            "input": {
                "type": "option",
                "vertical": false,
                "options": [
                    {
                        "text": "Next",
                        "value": "next",
                        "action": "q.dialogue.set_page('page2');"
                    }
                ]
            }
        },
        {
            "id": "page2",
            "speaker": "npc",
            "lines": [
                {
                    "type": "expression",
                    "expression": "'Mmm, ' + q.player.username + ', ¿eh?';"
                }
            ],
            "input": {
                "type": "option",
                "vertical": false,
                "options": [
                    {
                        "text": "Next",
                        "value": "next",
                        "action": "q.dialogue.set_page('page3');"
                    }
                ]
            }
        },
        {
            "id": "page3",
            "speaker": "npc",
            "lines": [
                "¿Sabes qué? Yo soy quien desarrolló el sistema para transferir Pokémon."
            ],
            "input": {
                "type": "option",
                "vertical": false,
                "options": [
                    {
                        "text": "Next",
                        "value": "next",
                        "action": "q.dialogue.set_page('page4');"
                    }
                ]
            }
        },
        {
            "id": "page4",
            "speaker": "npc",
            "lines": [
                "Pero no podría haberlo hecho yo solo. Por ejemplo, ¿conoces la región de Hoenn?"
            ],
            "input": {
                "type": "option",
                "vertical": false,
                "options": [
                    {
                        "text": "Next",
                        "value": "next",
                        "action": "q.dialogue.set_page('page5');"
                    }
                ]
            }
        },
        {
            "id": "page5",
            "speaker": "npc",
            "lines": [
                "Una chica llamada Lanette, de Hoenn, hizo que el Sistema de Almacenamiento Pokémon fuera más fácil de usar."
            ],
            "input": {
                "type": "option",
                "vertical": false,
                "options": [
                    {
                        "text": "Next",
                        "value": "next",
                        "action": "q.dialogue.set_page('page6');"
                    }
                ]
            }
        },
        {
            "id": "page6",
            "speaker": "npc",
            "lines": [
                "Mis amigos de todo el mundo están trabajando juntos para mejorar los sistemas de intercambio y almacenamiento de Pokémon."
            ],
            "input": {
                "type": "option",
                "vertical": false,
                "options": [
                    {
                        "text": "Next",
                        "value": "next",
                        "action": "q.dialogue.set_page('page7');"
                    }
                ]
            }
        },
        {
            "id": "page7",
            "speaker": "npc",
            "lines": [
                "Tengo que volver deprisa a Ciudad Trigal para ver a mi familia. ¡Adiós!"
            ],
            "input": {
                "type": "option",
                "vertical": false,
                "options": [
                    {
                        "text": "Close",
                        "value": "close",
                        "action": [
                            "q.run_command('tag ' + q.player.username + ' add Dialogue204');",
                            "q.run_command('tag ' + q.player.username + ' remove InDialogue');",
                            "q.run_command('scoreboard players set ' + q.player.username + ' TriggerCommand 93');",
                            "q.dialogue.close();"
                        ]
                    }
                ]
            }
        }
    ]
}